programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Luna-Loo and Tiki have a fight when they are playing with building blocks. They both storm off. Bramble tries to help them make peace with each other, and asks Miss Olivia for help. She prepares a special extracurricular activity for Tiki and Luna-Loo. They have to cooperate with each other to overcome obstacles and win the prize. When they finally get the prize, they realize the importance of teamwork.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: A Father’s Love & See the Signs
programme.desc: Babu is unhappy because his father doesn’t compliment him at Parents Day like the other parents. He thinks Barbara is very considerate when he’s learning paper cut in the bears’ house. Babu get blisters from the pair of scissors that is too big for his hand. When he gets home, he’s disappointed to find out his father doesn’t say much about his hand. He goes to take a nap while his father leaves home for work. When his friends come over to his home, however, they find out Babu’s dad have made many thoughtful gadgets for him. He even leaves a special pair of scissors especially made for Babu. Babu realizes that his father loves him in his own way.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Luna-Loo’s mom is going out for a trip. Her dad grows some flowers, intending to give her mom a surprise when she comes back. Luna-Loo wants to grow some flowers for her mom too, and gets a small lily from her father. She sees some wild flowers can grow very well without anyone tending them, so she decides not to take care of the orchid. The flower looks withered after just a few days. Luna-Loo realizes she needs to put in effort to gain something. She starts to take good care of the lily, which begins to grow well. At last she’s able to present her beautiful flowers to her mom when she comes back.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: Ernie Jo’s Gifts & The Paper Boats
programme.desc: Ernie Jo makes a wooden vase, but only Tiki likes it. Ernie Jo is glad Tiki likes weird things just like him. So Ernie Jo gives Tiki a lot of gifts. However, Tiki doesn’t have enough room for those gifts, so he exchanges those gifts for bananas with his friends. Ernie Jo is very angry when he finds out what happens. Tiki realizes his mistake and exchange his gifts back. Ernie Jo the trouble he causes and forgives him. The cubs finally decide to share their gifts with one another.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The two watchmen land on earth and read out the royal edict to the Kitchen God. The Kitchen God takes over the edict with reverence and awe and follows them onto a mass of cloud heading for the Heaven. They look down at the village on the way and find the masses offering sacrifice to the Kitchen God, praying for happiness and good fortune.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: After travelling miles of the sacred Heaven, the Kitchen God comes to the magnificent Hall of Miraculous Mist in the Golden-gated Cloud Palace. He poses a “V” (stands for victory) gesture with Aquila in front of the palace and asks Sonar to draw a portrait of them to mark the occasion. Shortly after, a lowly clerk comes over and brings the Kitchen God into the palace.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The Jade Emperor orders Aquila and Sonar to come down to earth and assist the Kitchen God with the task. Meanwhile, Rascal the rat finds the royal edict in the Kitchen God’s house and considers it a good opportunity to change the destinies of his family and himself. Rascal hides the edict to keep other animals from seeing it while the Kitchen God sees through his ruse and tries to recapture the edict. They get into an argument and start to scramble for the edict. Just then, Aquila and Sonar break into the house and join the scramble for the royal edict immediately. In the midst of chaos, the royal edict drops into a censer and is burned into ashes.

programme.title: Origins Of The Twelve
programme.desc: The Kitchen God, Rascal, and the two watchmen stand helplessly in front of the censer. Suddenly, a beam of golden light comes from the hearth and the royal edict floats up to the sky. The edict is made public and the news about the upcoming guardian tournament spreads like wildfire. The Kitchen God feels very remorseful for not keeping the secret. However, Aquila says that in that case they don’t need to worry about where to look for the competitors because all the masters will gather at Mount Tai from every corner of the village at that time.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is taking a stroll around the Marsh when all of a sudden a giant “owl” falls from the sky. Fearing that the scary bird would devour him, Joe hides himself behind a big rock. Bartle Bee passes by and finds something wrong about this furious “owl”. After a close examination, he discovers that this is not a bird but a paper kite. To fly the kite, Joe slides down a slope to help the kite gain altitude. The kite soars into the sky, taking Joe along on an exciting flight. At first, the fact that he’s ten feet off the ground frightens Joe Croaker. But as he manages to keep the kite under control, he finds himself fascinated by the midair adventure. Joe flies his “glider” and snatches the cheese from Cosmo, which makes the latter really angry. Joe gets completely carried away, when the kite flies into a desert scattered with cacti and becomes out of hand. In the end, Joe crashes in a huge cactus with his “glider”.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is casting about desperately for something to fill his empty stomach. Luckily for him, he finds some biscuits in a large can. So he jumps right into the can and gobbles up all the biscuits. But after the feast, the frog finds himself unable to get out of the can with an overstuffed belly. He tries all sorts of avenues and finally manages to hop up to the top. Suddenly, the can starts to roll down a slope. Joe freaks out inside the running can and cries for help, which is heard by Cosmo and Bartle Bee who happen to play nearby. They attempt to put a stop to the crazy can, but to no avail. At last, the can is halted on the edge of a cliff. Just when the Bartle Bee and his friends think they are safe, a rock comes running down, knocking the can down into the river. Fortunately enough, the three of them are saved by a large lotus leaf.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Bartle Bee finds a flowering plant in the forest. It is so good-looking that when Bartle Bee leaves, Joe Croaker brings it home and plants it in his back yard. The frog loves the plant and does not allow anyone except himself to touch it. But Cosmo still gets a nimble off one flower petal and the fly becomes extremely aggressive. Cosmo beats Joe Croaker up and makes the frog do his chores and give him massage.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo finds a discarded solar-powered toy car in the bush. He decides to keep it as a desirable toy. He shows off his new acquisition to Joe Croaker, who is immediately taken with the car as well. Joe Croaker seizes the car from Cosmo and tries to tug it home. As noon comes, the solar-powered car harnesses enough energy from the sun and starts to run on its own. Joe Croaker ties the car to a little tree, trying to keep it still. But fully charged with solar energy, the car breaks free of the restraint and takes Joe Croaker on an exciting road trip. Though a bit scared, Joe gets off on this wild car adventure. He snatches Cosmo’s cheese on the way. The car runs wild again and plunges into a pond, drowning Joe Croaker as well. Cosmo catches up, only to find his cheese cake gone under water.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo spots a paper boat on the stream. He picks two fine leaves as paddles and begins to go around in his boat. Flutterby is interested in the boat and she asks if she can join Cosmo. Cosmo refuses and Flutterby decides to make one boat on her own. She selects a large leaf and bends it into a boat.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Briar and Tiki chases their kite to Old Billy’s vegetable patch, and accidentally trample the vegetables. Although they try to correct the deed, but it just get worse. They try to avoid Old Billy in school and hesitate to apologize to him, for fear Old Billy will be angry. Briar tries to get Tiki and apologize to Old Billy. The old man tells them he’s going to the vegetable field to grow new vegetables. Briar and Tiki help him out. At last, they tell Old Billy the truth. The old man doesn’t get angry. Instead, he thinks they are responsible kids.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Luna-Loo doesn’t want to keep her old or broken toys, and asks her parents to buy her new ones. So she secretly throws away her old toys. When she visits Violet’s home, however, she finds out her friends treasure her toys very much, and remembers the good times she has spent with her toys. Then it rains. Luna-Loo quickly goes outside to find her toys with Violet but can’t find them. She’s feels regret. The next morning, she’s surprised to find out that all her toys are back. It turns out her mom picks up those toys, cleans and mends them. Luna-Loo realizes her mistake and thanks her mom. Violet and Vick come to Luna-Loo’s home and help her modify some old toys. Everyone is happy.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: Summoning the Sun & The Frog Friends
programme.desc: Luna-Loo stays at Violet’s home for the night. They borrow a toy car from Vick powered by solar energy. However, the car runs out of power at night. They are disappointed to find out the sun has already set. They decide to summon the sun. First they to use some “magic spells”, then an ice cream to “entice” the sun to come out. They even mimic the sound of roosters to try to call for the sun. The sun never comes out. Instead, Violet’s parents are woken by the noise. Through a little experiment, they explain to the kids about solar rotation and the switch of night and day.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Briar and Bramble discover that Old Billy’s office smells bad. They decide to help him get rid of the awful smell. They try to collect some fresh clean air from a flower field with bottles, and bring the air to the office. However, it’s hard to tell whether the fragrance is really inside the bottles. So they decide to use balloons to collect the scent. However, a little hedgehog accidentally pops the balloons when he tries to help them. Old Billy sees them and tells them that the stinky smell will go away if they keep good ventilation in the office.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is frightened upon spying what he believes to be a monster strolling around the pond. He soon realizes that the “monster” is actually a duck, but can’t work out that it’s in fact a toy duck. Assuming that this Rubber Ducky of Death is scheming to occupy his place, Joe Croaker flips out and decides to teach it a good lesson. He bullies the Rubber Ducky of Death until Bartle Bee sweeps it away. Bartle Bee is determined to rescue what he too, sadly, sees as a real—if unresponsive—duck. Joe gives chase to the two runaways, and they tangle with each other. During the confrontation, Bartle Bee accidentally gives the air-filled toy duck a prick with his sting, causing it to deflate and fly away. Still in the dark, Bartle Bee blames the disappearance of the poor little “creature” on Joe Croaker.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker finds a balloon dinosaur among the grass. The frog has no idea what he has discovered and he really panics at this “dinosaur” that is many times his own size. Joe Croaker begins to attack the balloon with pebbles he picks up from the ground. One of the pebbles bounces off the balloon and hits Bartle Bee’s honey jar on the ground. Though Joe Croaker tells Bartle Bee that he has nothing to do with the broken honey jar, the bee is smart enough to figure it out by himself.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo eats up all the food Joe Croaker has obtained, which puts the latter into a violate passion. And his mockery about Joe Croaker’s inability to fly adds fuel to fire. The hot-air balloons floating in the sky inspire the frog, who then manages to put together one with all the parts he collects from the garbage can. Flying with the ill-made balloon, Joe Croaker grabs the food from Cosmo and endeavors to catch the fly. But the balloon is too slow for Cosmo, so Joe plays dead to bamboozle Cosmo, who falls for it and ends up being caught. Just at that moment, the candle in the balloon exhausts itself. Both Joe Croaker and Cosmo fall to the ground, where the frog resumes his chase after his little foe.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker comes across a roly-poly toy when he is trying to get some candy near a dumpster. It’s a big smiling face doll. But the frog has no knowledge of what he is facing. He sees the roly-poly as a potential threat to him and the Marsh. Joe Croaker challenges the toy and attempts to take it down. The frog fails and finally he uses a rope to tie the roly-poly toy up.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: As the dung balls keep piling up, McBroom finds himself short of energy to get his work done all by himself. At Bartle Bee’s suggestion, he puts up a recruitment ad to look for someone to help him. The handsome benefits offered on this job allure many insects over, including Hercules Beetle, Snout Beetle and Bartle Bee. To select the best out of the three candidates, McBroom put them on a series of tests where Hercules Beetle stands out to win the position as McBroom’s assistant. Much to McBroom’s disappointment, however, his employee turns out to be quite lazy. So he has to give Hercules Beetle the sack and send him home.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: It's all Because of the Lollipop
programme.desc: Joe Croaker finds himself a treat of a large lollipop. After gorging on it, Joe places the hollowed lollipop around his neck and starts to toy with it. Not until he tries in vain to remove the lolly does he realize that he is stuck in it. As the lolly around Joe’s neck begins to melt, it becomes sticky and attracts many leaves to it. Joe looks just like a scary monster in that leafy lollipop! The other bug buddies are all frightened at the sight of Joe, mistaking him for the ruthless monster that has swallowed Joe alive. To revenge their good friend, the folks conceive a plan to capture “the monster”. Joe is cornered into a big ditch, where the lollipop around his neck is broken apart by McBroom’s dung ball. Not until then do the folks realize that the “monster” is none other than Joe Croaker! Just when the frog is about to fly off the handle, his buddies have already made themselves scarce.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is intrigued when he sees Niddy travels with her silk. The frog believes he might be able to do the same.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.sub-title: Joe's got a Fish Bone in His Throat
programme.desc: Joe Croaker is on the prowl for food and the fish obtained by Cosmo makes his mouth water. As is typical of Joe Croaker the greedy bully frog, he snatches the fish from Cosmo and quickly swallows it whole. But such voracity only results in the bones being stuck in Joe’s throat. Seeing Joe in great pain, Cosmo is in panic and at a loss what to do to help. At that moment, Bartle Bee happens to pass by and offers Joe his nectar to help ease the pain. But it fails to work. Then Bartle suggests two possible solutions he learnt from books, which are ramming down the bones with a bun and dissolving them with vinegar. Cosmo and Joe hurry to the Garbage can and score both a bun and a bottle of vinegar, but it turns out neither way helps remove the bones from Joe’s throat. In the end, proposed again by the resourceful Bartle Bee, they hang Joe Croaker upside down and succeed in swinging the bones out of Joe’s throat.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Fed up living in his shabby can house, Cosmo decides to find himself a sleek, cozy new place. First he is taken with the fancy-looking paper box with pretty patterns and good light, but Bartle Bee reminds him of its vulnerability to rain in wet seasons. So he keeps on searching his dream home. Then, a crystal clear glass jar commands Cosmo’s attention. Just when he is about to make it his new abode, the mole cricket’s warning against this heat-accumulating material discourages him from settling down there. So Cosmo has to look for other alternatives. Then he discovers a large magnet which he uses to attract pieces of parts together and make them into a solidly constructed iron house. After a long day’s rushing about, Cosmo retires to rest at his pleasant new home. But something bad happens. A coin is drawn to the magnet house and blocks the exit. Trapped inside his own house, Cosmo shouts for help, which invites Joe Croaker over. The frog agrees to help him out on the condition that Cosmo offers him both service and food. But instead of getting Cosmo out, Joe accidentally sets a large iron lid running, which crashes into the magnet house. Luckily enough, Cosmo is able to survive with the help of the mole cricket. In the end, Joe Croaker has to compensate Cosmo by offering him his service instead.

programme.title: Pondemonium
programme.desc: Cosmo has got a nice ice cream postage stamp, which is overheard by Joe Croaker. The thought of the tasty ice cream tempts the amphibian into a plot to steal the stamp from Cosmo. He tails Cosmo, and tries in vain to grab the stamp. Tired from the flight, Cosmo rests himself upon a branch, covering himself with the stamp. Seeing this as a good opportunity, Joe employs every possible method known to him to try to score the stamp. But none of them really works. Then the green vines hanging down the tree inspire him. He uses the vines to climb up and reaches out for the stamp. He then falls off onto the ground along with the stamp. Just when Joe assumes he has secured the ice cream stamp for good, a gust of wind blows it up to the tree again. Cosmo wakes up and joyfully takes the stamp back home.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac

When they finally get the prize, they realize the importance of teamwork.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.sub-title: A Father’s Love & See the Signs
programme.desc: Babu is unhappy because his father doesn’t compliment him at Parents Day like the other parents. When he gets home, he’s disappointed to find out his father doesn’t say much about his hand. He goes to take a nap while his father leaves home for work. When his friends come over to his home, however, they find out Babu’s dad have made many thoughtful gadgets for him. He even leaves a special pair of scissors especially made for Babu. Babu realizes that his father loves him in his own way.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac
programme.desc: Luna-Loo’s mom is going out for a trip. Her dad grows some flowers, intending to give her mom a surprise when she comes back. She sees some wild flowers can grow very well without anyone tending them, so she decides not to take care of the orchid. The flower looks withered after just a few days. Luna-Loo realizes she needs to put in effort to gain something. She starts to take good care of the lily, which begins to grow well. At last she’s able to present her beautiful flowers to her mom when she comes back.

programme.title: Masters of the Zodiac

The toughest one: Don't tell Dale you have it. Can Matt afford to buy the bike and get it running in time for the race without Dale seeing it? Will Dale even get his broken bike started? And if they ever get to race, will Matt exact his revenge?

programme.title: What's In the Barn?
programme.desc: Built in the mid-60’s by eccentric engineer “Wild Bill” Gelbke, the Road Dog was, and still is, the largest motorcycle ever built. It utilized aircraft tubing, Corvette disc brakes, and a Chevy truck differential to keep it stable. The one-off creation disappeared when Gelbke did in 1978. Outflanked once when the bike was spotted and sold to a private collector in 1995, Dale has vowed to locate the machine and make Wheels Through Time its final resting place.

programme.title: What's In the Barn?

programme.title: What's In the Barn?

programme.title: What's In the Barn?

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz

Side mirrors for a muscle car, building a better battery, and keeping your air flowing through carbon fiber vents fill out the parts bin. Take a look back at the kid with the dream. Follow the design and fabrication. See what happens when the military tribute vehicle rolls out and conquers the road! This episode is gonna be epic. It’s been a long road, but anything worth doing well is worth the wait. This week, the wait is over. Sergeant Rock Lives!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.sub-title: On the Road & Unicure Spray Booths
programme.desc: Things are rockin’ and rollin’ in and out of the GearZ garage. Stacey hits the road to find a project build that will get gear heads buzzing. He ends up with an ’81 Camaro and some awesome stories from the seller. If you’re talking project vehicles, you’ve got to talk paint! And Stacey does just that with folks from Unicure, who specialize in paint booths and helping you get set up for that all important paint job. The V-8 Interceptor is back from a trip to Stainless works, where a custom exhaust system was made for the big Boss Nine engine. Things are about to get loud, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.sub-title: The Return of Heavy Metal & Snowcat
programme.desc: Stacey and the GearZ crew roll in an old favorite: Heavy Metal. The coolest hotrod tow truck is back in the garage and ready for a facelift. Our good friends at the Hot Rod Institute drop by and talk shop with Stacey about his plans for the paint and fab work needed to get this bad boy looking good and back on the road. Fresh from the sandblaster, the snowcat reveals the scars that were under the skin. And with the drive train out, Stacey walks through the importance of replacing gaskets, seals and checking for wear and tear before stuffing that engine, transmission and skid steer rear end back into the cat. There’s a whole lot going on this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Every gear head has a secret: they all want to drive like McQueen in Bullitt, or Vin Diesel in The Fast And The Furious. But when the heat gets turned up, even some really good drivers can’t keep up. That’s when you bring in the Stunt Double! This week Stacey sits down with legendary Hollywood stunt man Ian Quinn to talk crashing cars and keeping actors out of harms way. There’s also a new project in the garage: The Stunt Double, a build inspired by the 80’s tv show The Fall Guy, and sure to get all four wheels off the ground before Stacey’s done with it. Sparks are going to fly and you know we’re gonna have a good time this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: Seems like you can’t go more than a block these days without running into someone whose had some work done on their face. Well, here at the GearZ garage, Stacey believes in facelifts too. Just to prove it, he’s taken on a 1981 Camaro and sharpened his scalpel to perform an automotive nose job. Just wait till you see him whack of the old rubber nose and replace it with a 71’ rally sport front end! Now that’s what we call a facelift. Plenty of people said it couldn’t be done, but that’s just the kind of challenge Stacey is up for. Plenty of sparks are gonna fly, this week on GearZ.

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: They say that true change comes from within… Well, this week Stacey turns his attention to the interior of the Stunt Double. The old, crusty junk hits the floor and our Fall Guy inspired build gets a new look: from painting trim and door panels, to a new bench seat. Man o’ man, this truck is starting to look completely different. A shower of sparks lights up the garage as Stacey demonstrates how to make a bracket that mounts our new bench seat to the truck while using the stock seat adjustment. It’s a tour de force of aftermarket parts and salvaging what we’ve got, this week on GearZ!

programme.title: Stacey David's Gearz
programme.desc: When you’re putting together a project that’s inspired by a high-flying stunt truck, you know you’ve got to add some lift, and our Stunt Double gets the goods this week. The front and rear suspension get treated to a 6” lift to get that rig up in the air. But a good lift won’t do any good if the steering and frame can’t hold up, so Stacey shows you how Offroad Design has fixed some serious issues that many late model four-wheel drives encounter. Bed need to come off your truck, but the carriage bolts are rusted and spinning? Stacey’s got a fix for that too. There’s a lot going on, and we’ve got you covered, this week on GearZ.

programme.desc: Pitufina se convierte en reina por un dia en su cumpleanos. Sin embargo, la situacion se descontrola cuando Padre Tiempo se queda dormido y no cumple su cometido de terminar los dias. Los animos comienzan a calentarse entre los Pitufos, que estan cansados de trabajar. Papa Pitufo acude a despertar a Padre Tiempo y trae de vuelta la paz a la tierra de los Pitufos.

programme.title: La Estrella De La Suerte De Pitufina
programme.desc: Pitufina ha elegido su estrella de los deseos de la suerte y sera suya para siempre... mientras formule deseos que no sean egoistas. Pero Pitufina, con sus malas elecciones a la hora de hacer deseos, provoca que la estrella caiga del cielo y Gargamel quiere hacerse con ella...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Hogatha se disfraza de premio de oro para observar a los Pitufos y capturarlos para sus ingredientes de belleza. Vanidoso acaba convenciendola de que pruebe su receta y acaba cubierta de barro de vuelta a casa de Gargamel.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: El Costal Magico De Santa Claus
programme.desc: Si hay algo que desagrada a la malvada hechicera Clorhidris es la bondad y el amor propios de la Navidad. Trama un plan para robar el costal magico de Santa Claus, en el que transporta todos los juguetes que los ninos que se han portado bien reciben por Navidad. Sin embargo, no sabe que un enfurrunado Pitufo Grunon esta escondido dentro del saco.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Selwyn y Tallulah son un matrimonio de poderosos hechiceros. El problema es que estan todo el rato peleandose. La energia de sus discusiones esta formando una temible tormenta, y Papa Pitufo debe conseguir que hagan las paces antes de que la tormenta arrecie.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Unos lentes rosados llegan a manos de Pitufina y resultan ser un sucio truco de Gargamel.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En la antigua Mesopotamia, despues de que Pitufina se pinche en el dedo con la espina de una flor magica, todo lo que toca se transforma en una planta. ¿Podra Papa Pitufo salvarla de las malvadas flores de Babilonia?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Papa Pitufo le da a Pitufo Debilucho una crema especial para que la utilice y recupere su fuerza. Poco despues, recibe una condecoracion por sus heroicos actos de fortaleza, y su autoestima se dispara cuando se da cuenta de que la crema es simplemente mermelada de pitufrutas.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En la Aldea Pitufo hay un ataque de Mala Suerte y cien Pitufos deben bailar una danza magica para recuperar la buena fortuna, ¡pero solo hay 99 en la aldea! ¿Quien sera el centesimo Pitufo?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: ¡Pitufo Torpe ha desenterrado una extrana piedra! En ella, puede ver los eventos que van a suceder... ¡No obstante, conocer parte del futuro a veces trae mala suerte!

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Tenia que pasarle a Pitufo Filosofo. La quintaesencia de la pitufietiqueta, el epitome de la correccion, la personificacion de todas esas virtudes es, asumamoslo, aburrido y pretencioso. Y ahora, Pitufo Filosofo sufre la agonia de volverse... digamos que diferente. Sin embargo, esta en grave peligro...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos deben encontrar a una familia de conejos para tirar de su carroza durante el Festival de Otono. Gargamel ve la oportunidad de capturar a los pequenos seres azules y se disfraza de conejo gigante. ¿Conseguira atrapar a todos los Pitufos de un plumazo?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El rey Symphonium envia a su pelicano Satchelmouth para capturar a la orquesta de Pitufo Filosofo y llevar a todos hasta su isla. Pitufo Sonador se pone al timon de un barco y se hace a la mar para rescatarlos. Cuando Pitufo Sonador se marea, Pitufo Filosofo toma el mando y encabeza el equipo de rescate que libera a los Pitufos capturados.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Tenia que suceder. Tanto vivir solo y toda esa locura por capturar a los Pitufos finalmente se han cobrado su precio. Cuando el malvado mago se encuentra con la bruja Evelyn, cae rendido de amor. Haria lo que fuera por ella. Incluso salir a cazar Pitufos para ofrecerselos como regalo...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La nota que Papa Pitufo escribio avisando a los demas Pitufos para que vean un cometa esta rota. Al ser solo capaces de leer una parte, los Pitufos creen que es el fin del mundo. Todos planean como sera su ultimo dia, hasta que papa Pitufo regresa y clarifica el lio.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: La Primera Palabra De Bebe Pitufo
programme.desc: Los Pitufitos liberan a los Pitufos de las garras de Gargamel justo a tiempo para llevar a Bebe Pitufo a la ceremonia de su primera palabra. Bebe Pitufo pronuncia la palabra «Gargamel». Papa Pitufo afirma que esa palabra indica que Bebe Pitufo se convertira un dia en un gran lider, ya que significa que es consciente de los peligros de la vida.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Una vez al ano, Pitufo Goloso prepara un lote especial de caramelos de pitufrutas. Cada Pitufo recibe provisiones para un ano entero del dulce mas pitufantastico de todo el mundo. Pero ¿puede un Pitufo conseguir que sus provisiones le duren todo el ano? ¿Lo conseguira Pitufina?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Labrador se pregunta que hace una calabaza en el melonar, cuando deberia estar junto a los colinabos. Cuando Pitufo Labrador tira de la calabaza y la separa del suelo, libera a un genio que comienza a llamarle amo e insiste en concederle deseos. El ansia del genio, llamado Gourdy, por complacer a Pitufo Labrador hara que, mas que en una ayuda, se convierta en una molestia.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En el Dia de la Infelicidad, los Pitufos tienen que ser infelices para poder apreciar su felicidad durante el resto del ano. Gargamel inventa un detector de felicidad para encontrar a los Pitufos, pero lo usa justo el unico dia en el que los Pitufos no son felices. En su lugar, encuentra a una pareja de dragones felices y desata su ira.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Filosofo lo ha vuelto a hacer. Ademas, esta vez ha sido delante de Papa Pitufo. Ha pronunciado un hechizo que convierte todo en piedra. Todo, incluyendo a el mismo y a los demas Pitufos, asi como la aldea y muchos kilometros del bosque que hay alrededor. Afortunadamente, aparece Guillermo.

programme.title: La Carrera De Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Carpintero ha ideado un nuevo invento: el pitufimovil. Todos los Pitufos tienen su propio vehiculo personalizado y todos (o casi todos) disfrutan dando una vuelta en ellos. Sin embargo, el malvado mago Gargamel se aprovecha de la idea y empieza a causar problemas a los Pitufos...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Robotin se siente tan solo que, compadeciendose de el, Pitufo Carpintero le construye una companera. El problema es que PituforRobotinina no sabe que unicamente debe fijarse en su companero mecanico, o que debe evitar a Gargamel...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos llegan a Camelot, donde presencian varios sucesos: la traicionera Morgana Le Fey roba Excalibur, la espada magica, y transforma al mago Merlin, al rey Arturo y a Lancelot en indefensas victimas.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Durante una mision para interrumpir la fiesta de Halloween de los Pitufos, Gargamel y Hogatha consiguen capturar a Perezoso, el cual se ha vuelto rojo por un extrano capricho de la naturaleza. Papa Pitufo y los demas conseguiran liberar a Perezoso, y la Madre Naturaleza devolvera su color al pitufo.

programme.title: El Libro De Bromas De Bromista
programme.desc: Las cajas sorpresa de Pitufo Bromista ya no resultan divertidas para los demas Pitufos. Pitufo Bromista busca nuevas ideas en su «Gran libro de las bromas», pero esas ideas son aun peor recibidas en la aldea. Y entonces, Gargamel llega con algunas bromas de su propia cosecha...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La repulsiva bruja Hogata captura a Pitufina. Quiere robarle a la pequena belleza azul su cabello dorado. ¿Conseguiran salvar los Pitufos a su pequena companera antes de que sea demasiado tarde? ¿Lograra Hogata una cabellera como la de Pitufina?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Esta vez, Gargamel tiene un plan infalible. Sin hacer caso de la risa burlona de Azrael, el malvado hechicero ha perfeccionado una sustancia magica a la que ha llamado «polvo temerario», que convertira a todos los Pitufos en temerarios e intrepidos aventureros. ¿Caera Papa Pitufo en la trampa de Gargamel? ¿Atrapara su enemigo a todos los Pitufos? ¿Tendra esta historia un final feliz?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Hay una isla, no muy lejos de la costa de Espana, en la que pequenos seres viven en un estado permanente de guerra. Cuando Pitufo Goloso y Pitufo Filosofo caen en bandos distintos, la guerra da un giro a peor.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Sonador vera cumplido su deseo de ser un Astropitufo cuando Papa Pitufo le hechiza para quedarse dormido, transformando el paisaje y a los Pitufos en una fantasia galactica. Gargamel vigila de cerca las travesuras de los Pitufos desde su bola de cristal, pero el hechizo de Papa Pitufo tambien tiene efecto en el y le transporta hasta el centro de una tormenta.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Escocia, como todos sabemos, esta repleta de fantasmas que vagan por los castillos. Los Pitufos se topan con el alma perdida de un viejo gaitero, que les pide ayuda para recuperar el caballo que le robaron.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Un terrible gigante ayuda a Gargamel a capturar a los Pitufos para hacer una rica sopa, pero tendra que enfrentar a Papa Pitufo primero.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En el Dia de la Infelicidad, los Pitufos tienen que ser infelices para poder apreciar su felicidad durante el resto del ano. Gargamel inventa un detector de felicidad para encontrar a los Pitufos, pero lo usa justo el unico dia en el que los Pitufos no son felices. En su lugar, encuentra a una pareja de dragones felices y desata su ira.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Goloso es un gran conocedor de la buena comida. Sin embargo, en la antigua Roma descubre un nuevo y delicioso plato y decide que quiere aprender la receta. Para ello, Pitufo Goloso primero debe ganar un concurso.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Una vez mas, el infalible plan de Gargamel para atrapar a los Pitufos ha fracasado. Los Pitufos aprovechan para gastarle una broma: disfrazados de pequenos angeles azules, le ensenaran a enmendar su conducta...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En la antigua Mesopotamia, despues de que Pitufina se pinche en el dedo con la espina de una flor magica, todo lo que toca se transforma en una planta. ¿Podra Papa Pitufo salvarla de las malvadas flores de Babilonia?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: En la antigua China, la fortuna se esconde en las galletas del Pitufo Goloso, y Pitufo Filosofo es el escritor. Es una oportunidad demasiado buena para hacer travesuras como para que Pitufo Bromista la desperdicie.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Fortachon tiene un monton de cualidades: masculinidad, encanto, una sonrisa cautivadora y un bonito tatuaje en el brazo. Quiza eso es lo que provoca que una orangutana gigante de la jungla se enamore de el.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La Aldea Pitufa esta protegida de los intrusos gracias a un hechizo que impide que nadie pueda llegar hasta ella, salvo que un Pitufo le conduzca hasta alli. Sin embargo, el hechizo terminara en unas horas y el malvado mago Gargamel esta al acecho.

programme.title: La Pitufivision De Genio
programme.desc: Pitufo Minero rebusca bajo todas las piedras y, gracias a ello, descubre un cristal que transmite imagenes. Esto permite a Pitufo Carpintero inventar la pitufivision y, desde ese momento, los Pitufos pueden ver todas las mananas los entrenamientos de Pitufo Fortachon, los informes de las cosechas de Pitufo Labrador e incluso el programa de Pitufo Filosofo. Pero ¿quien podria haberlo imaginado? ¡El malvado mago Gargamel se aprovecha de la pitufivision para atrapar Pitufos!

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Selwyn y Tallulah son un matrimonio de poderosos hechiceros. El problema es que estan todo el rato peleandose. La energia de sus discusiones esta formando una temible tormenta, y Papa Pitufo debe conseguir que hagan las paces antes de que la tormenta arrecie.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Cuando los Pitufos llegan a la antigua China, descubren que el emperador nino corre peligro de ser depuesto. ¿Y por quien? ¡Por el malvado Garg-Fu-Yun, que quiere hacerse con el trono del nino!

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: El Gran Sueno De Papa Pitufo
programme.desc: El sabio y prudente Papa Pitufo, sin el cual el pequeno pueblo azul estaria indefenso, sufre la mordedura del Monstruo del Sueno en el antiguo Japon. Cae dormido y, para despertarle, los Pitufos emprenden un viaje...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: El Pitufo Que Queria Ser Rey
programme.desc: Pitufo Sonador anhela convertirse en rey despues de leer una historia sobre reyes. Mientras esta en su barco, cae a traves de un remolino y llega a una tierra de pequenos seres que creen que Pitufo Sonador es su rey, desaparecido hace mucho tiempo. Cuando se enfrenta a los Norfnangs, los enemigos de esos pequenos seres, descubre que no son terrorificos en absoluto. Pitufo Sonador se da un golpe en la cabeza y descubre al despertar que todo habia sido un sueno, aunque encuentra en su gorro una joya identica a las que extraian esos pequenos seres de su mina.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Creyendo que Bebe Pitufo es un duende, dos cazadores furtivos lo secuestran e intentan que el pequeno les diga donde ha escondido la olla de oro. Papa Pitufo organiza a todos para atacar a los villanos con tartas de pitufrutas y lograr que Bebe Pitufo pueda escapar.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Es la noche de los fantasmas y todos los Pitufos se preparan para la elegante fiesta de disfraces... pero Pitufo Filosofo se hace con el libro de magia de Papa Pitufo y todos los Pitufos se transforman en criaturas horrendas, aunque divertidas. No obstante, el peligro acecha...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La racha de 200 anos de buena suerte de los Pitufos se interrumpe bruscamente cuando Gargamel encuentra el castillo de la Dama de la Fortuna, la encierra en una mazmorra y comienza a manipular su rueda de la suerte. ¿Se quedaran de brazos cruzados los Pitufos ante ese cambio de fortuna?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Ser Papa Pitufo da muchas alegrias, pero tambien tiene algunas desventajas. Por ejemplo, que alguien te interrumpa cada cinco minutos, incluso cuando estas en medio de delicados experimentos magicos. Eso hace que Papa Pitufo se plantee si seria posible que un Pitufo le sustituyera y se encargara de tomar las decisiones...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Baltasar lleva a Denisa con Gargamel para que este haga de canguro. Sin embargo, Gargamel pierde a Denisa en el bosque y esta se encuentra con Sasita y se hace amiga de ella. Sasita y Denisa colaboran para sacar a los Pitufos del caldero de Gargamel y demostrar que la valentia no es cuestion de tamano.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Genio ha decidido dedicarse al bienestar de los demas Pitufos. Va a curarles de todos sus males...con la ayuda del malvado Gargamel!

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Nadie le cree al Abuelo Pitufo cuando habla de junglas y sabanas lejanas, repletas de gatos salvajes gigantes, caballos a rayas, comedores de hojas de cuello largo y extranas tribus... Tan solo algunos Pitufitos dan cierto credito a sus historias. Pero, cuando Abuelo Pitufo escucha en el bosque el sonido del tambor real magico, un instrumento capaz de domar bestias salvajes, se lanza a la aventura para demostrar que no es un contador de historias al que el cerebro le juega malas pasadas.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: El Secreto Del Pantano De Las Sombras
programme.desc: Pitufo Grunon, que odia todo, detesta especialmente su propia fiesta de cumpleanos, por lo que decide esconderse en el Pantano de las Sombras. Alli encontrara extranos seres y vivira aventuras aun mas extranas mientras los demas Pitufos le buscan...

programme.title: El Amo Escrupulo
programme.desc: Pitufo Labrador es el reticente amo de un genio llamado Gourdy, cuyo entusiasmo por ser servicial es quiza algo excesivo. Tras un nuevo incidente provocado por el exceso de celo de Gourdy, Pitufo Labrador le dice algo que no deberia haber dicho y Gourdy desaparece. ¿Y a que no adivinas quien lo encuentra? En efecto: Escrupuloso, el aprendiz del malvado mago Gargamel. ¿Y quien podria arrebatar a Gourdy de las manos de Escrupuloso, sino el propio Gargamel?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: Una Choza No Es Un Hogar
programme.desc: Gargamel desea tener una choza mas grande, y recurre al Gran libro de hechizos para conjurar un nuevo hogar. Sin embargo, todos sus hechizos le salen del reves y esto le convence de que no hay ningun sitio como el hogar.

programme.title: Llamen Al Doctor Pitufo
programme.desc: Tal como su propio nombre indica, Pitufo Aficionado es incapaz de concentrarse en una actividad concreta. Pasa de una cosa a otra con tremenda facilidad y nunca termina lo que empieza. Pero, de repente, descubre que le apasiona la profesion medica. Pitufo Aficionado quiere convertirse en doctor y todos los Pitufos, con Papa Pitufo a la cabeza, van a ayudarle a cumplir su deseo.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: ¿Que, o quien, es ese extrano ser que hay en el bosque? Se asemeja vagamente a un Pitufo, pero castanetea los dientes como la ardilla que parece acompanarle... ¿y por que habla Papa Pitufo acerca del Pitufito Perdido?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos aman las trufas y las trufas son de los Trolls. No sera nada facil que los pitufitos azules tengan un banquete.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: La encantadora Allura posee una esfera magica muy especial cuya energia, segun ella misma dice, puede levantar el animo e inspirar a aquellos faltos de inspiracion. Todo lo que hay que hacer es sostener la esfera con las manos... Es cierto que la esfera fomenta la inspiracion, pero solo hasta cierto punto. Sin embargo, sus efectos secundarios pueden ser muy peligrosos, tal como descubren los Pitufos cuando se hacen adictos a la esfera...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: ¿Que es esa pequena luna que ha llegado del cielo? Es un globo de barro cubierto de crateres y habitado por los Lodosos, una familia de criaturas que vienen del cielo y comen y salpican barro. No todos los Pitufos demuestran entusiasmo por los visitantes...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Creyendo que Bebe Pitufo es un duende, dos cazadores furtivos lo secuestran e intentan que el pequeno les diga donde ha escondido la olla de oro. Papa Pitufo organiza a todos para atacar a los villanos con tartas de pitufrutas y lograr que Bebe Pitufo pueda escapar.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos serian un delicioso manjar para el malvado mago Gargamel si no fuera por dos cosas: son dificiles de atrapar y tambien muy pequenos. Ahora bien, si hubiera una formula que permitiera transformar a esos pequenos aperitivos de bocado en grandes y jugosas raciones azules... Gargamel ha tenido una idea...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: El huevo magico de Gargamel termina en la Aldea de los Pitufos donde los pequenitos azules piden un deseo loco tras otro lo que provoca un caos total. Papa Pitufo tiene que burlar a Gargamel y Giganton antes de que sus pociones magicas deshagan los estragos causados por el huevo y regrese la pitufarmonia.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Un hechizo ha alterado las cajas sorpresa explosivas de Pitufo Bromista. Imagina la cara de desconcierto que se le queda a este guason cuando se da cuenta de que todas las sorpresas que entrega a otros incautos Pitufos en realidad contienen regalos. ¡Se acabaron las explosiones, las bromas y la diversion! Y a eso se le une su poco envidiable posicion como el Pitufo mas popular de la aldea, rodeado de admiradores que no cesan de pedirle mas obsequios...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Los Pitufos conocen a un elfo del bosque, que les ensena la lengua de signos despues de que Gargamel les administre una pocion de enmudecimiento.

programme.title: Las Crisis Del Fango
programme.desc: El Rey Verrugoso entra en panico porque la cosecha de fango esta siendo un fracaso. Decide capturar a Pitufo Labrador, el mayor experto en agricultura del mundo, para resolver su problema. Pitufo Labrador instala un sistema de riego y salva la cosecha. Despues, escapa en una burbuja y regresa con los demas Pitufos.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Una de las cosas con las que mas disfruta Abuelo Pitufo es contar una buena historia de miedo, y a la mayoria de los Pitufos les encantan. Sin embargo, las cosas se complican para Pitufo Filosofo cuando Abuelo Pitufo habla de las pitufianimas y estas comienzan a acecharle...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Cuando los Pitufos llegan al monte Olimpo, se encuentran con Zeus, que no demuestra precisamente tener calma olimpica. Va a enviar a su timido hijo en una expedicion para encontrar el vellocino de oro. Y los Pitufos le ayudaran...

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Hogatha se disfraza de premio de oro para observar a los Pitufos y capturarlos para sus ingredientes de belleza. Vanidoso acaba convenciendola de que pruebe su receta y acaba cubierta de barro de vuelta a casa de Gargamel.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.sub-title: La Epidemia De La Tos Saltarina
programme.desc: Gargamel propaga un extrano germen por el bosque que hace toser a todos sin parar. Bebe Pitufo es la primera victima y todo el pueblo esta muy preocupado...Afortunadamente, Papa Pitufo cree conocer la solucion.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Gargamel esta decidido a sobrevolar la Aldea Pitufa para atrapar a un Pitufo y llevarlo a la Convencion de los Magos, e invoca a su libro de hechizos para que le ayude. Esto da lugar a una serie de divertidos contratiempos con su maquina voladora, y Gargamel vuelve a convertirse en el hazme reir de la Convencion de los Magos.

programme.title: La Formula Aniquiladora
programme.desc: Existe una palabra magica aterradora. Cuando pronuncias esa palabra hacia algo o alguien, ¡haces que se desvanezca en la nada! ¿Podran los Pitufos anular su malvado poder antes de que Gargamel se apropie de ella?

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Gargamel esta decidido a sobrevolar la Aldea Pitufa para atrapar a un Pitufo y llevarlo a la Convencion de los Magos, e invoca a su libro de hechizos para que le ayude. Esto da lugar a una serie de divertidos contratiempos con su maquina voladora, y Gargamel vuelve a convertirse en el hazme reir de la Convencion de los Magos.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Mientras los Pitufos se preparan para el Festival de las Estrellas, Gargamel consigue infiltrar entre ellos una criatura que emite un olor a podrido tan intenso que le permitira encontrar facilmente la Aldea Pitufa. Papa Pitufo se da cuenta de que la criatura maloliente es de otro planeta, y manda a Plumifero que la devuelva a su hogar antes de que Gargamel les encuentre.

programme.title: Los Pitufos
programme.desc: Pitufo Curioso ha tenido una idea: ¿por que no imprimir un boletin con todas las noticias de la aldea? Esta seguro de que sus cotilleos sobre los Pitufos interesaran a todos los lectores. Pero las cosas no salen exactamente segun lo previsto cuando Papa Pitufo encuentra superpitufrutas.

programme.title: Los Pitufos

programme.title: Morelos
programme.desc: The movie portraits the last years in the life of José María Morelos y Pavón, Mexican heroe, who after escaping the siege of his enemies takes one of the most important cities of Mexico. However, having more than half of the Mexican territory in his hands, he insists on taking over the Acapulcos harbor while the royal troops rearrange themselves, grow stronger and slowly gain get territory back.

programme.title: El túnel de los huesos
programme.desc: Based on a real event, this is the spectacular escape of seven prisoners in 1991 from the Villa Devoto prison in Buenos Aires, Argentina. In the process of digging a tunnel to escape, they make a bizarre and frightening discovery just as they are about to break through to freedom. One escapee promises to report their findings when they are all free and once out, he pays his debt to “the tunnel of bones,”sharing their macabre story with a local journalist, and ultimately the world.

programme.title: Como te ves, me vi
programme.desc: The story presents a dysfunctional family, whose problems are accentuated by the difficult relationship between a father and his adolescent son. Narrated in two timelines, present and past, the director reflects on adulthood to recall that the father once was also young.

programme.title: 7 Soles
programme.desc: El Negro, a "pollero" hired to cross a group of undocumented immigrants to the United States, decides that this will be his last trip for the organization. He wants to get out of business. The chiefs suspect him and send a subaltern, "El Gavilán", to watch him. On the rugged crossing the polleros betrayed themselves, losing part of their human "cargo". The Negro escapes from his former partners and also from justice. El Gavilán returns unpunished to his work as a "hooker." Nothing stops the deadly machinery of human trafficking.

programme.title: El Paso
programme.desc: This is a story about the families of those that once were our eyes and our voice, but were threatened, and had to leave Mexico and forced to live in exile.

programme.title: El viaje de la nonna
programme.desc: A Mexican family, wanting to grant their Grandmother her last wish, embarks on a make believe trip to a small town in Italy ... in Mexico!

programme.title: Islam de Cuba
programme.desc: Three cubans converted to Islam live a new revolution that starts from personal choices and involves all their social dimensions.

Leo is going through a crisis with his couple Lorena and works 12 hours a day driving a taxi in Rosario city. The city is changing and that overwhelms him. Unexpectedly, a passenger fades out in his taxi.

programme.title: El ángel en el reloj
programme.desc: Un cuento de hadas sobre el tiempo y una chica que quiere detenerlo. Una película que apoya la investigación del cáncer infantil.

programme.title: Paraguay, droga y banana
programme.desc: A thrilling, incisive documentary that breaks down how a prominent drug trafficker’s settlement in Paraguay in the late ’60s set in motion a wave of rampant corruption, leaving no part of the country untouched.

programme.title: 180 Grados
programme.desc: Salvador Diaz is a skilled conman. For most of his years, he cheated others for a living... until he cheated the wrong man. After messing with Martin Soto, Salvador's life now lies in the hands (or rather, the knee) of Gasparotto, an injured sports star who's flawlessness in the playing field becomes the most important factor not only for 'bringing in the big bucks', but for claiming his life back.
